<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很抱歉，<delay20 />
我现在想一个人静静<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能请你暂时别来打扰我吗。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />先不要来打扰我了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在需要一点时间<delay20 />
独自一人沉下心来思考<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在不想和任何人说话<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你偶尔也会有<delay20 />
这种时候的，不是吗？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />盛开于附近的花朵，<delay20 />
不知不觉间凋零了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然我也不是每天都在照顾它，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我感觉得到，自己已经在<delay8 />不知不觉中<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />从它身上获得了许多的慰藉……<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果我能早些注意到，给它浇浇水就好了。<delay40 />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />人总是等到失去了之后，<delay20 />
才能感受到它对自己有多重要啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />和我说过，<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />“用不着每天都给植物浇水，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它们也会自己茁壮成长的”<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我疏忽大意了……<delay40 />
<anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />结果有一天，<delay8 />
它突然就枯萎了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />真的很可惜……</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />原来是这样</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是呀<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
虽然当时我手忙脚乱地给它浇了水，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但结果还是迟了那么一步<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算不需要每天照顾它，<delay20 />
我至少也该每隔一天
就给它浇一次水的<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且我也的确记不得，
最后一次给它浇水<delay8 /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是什么时候的事情了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的是做了件蠢事呀……<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
我现在没有心情和人聊天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请你让我暂时独处一会儿。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在不想见任何人。<delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能不能请你暂时<delay20 />
不要来打扰我？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="100" b="1" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在什么都不想听。<delay40 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为我的心里已经<delay20 />
装下了太多的悲伤……<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。<endTag a="100" b="1" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我竟会感觉如此悲伤……<delay20 />
就仿佛是心里<delay8 />
蒙上了一层浓厚的雾霾<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="203_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />抱歉</message>
	<message label="203_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />嗯……</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你愿意道歉的话，<delay20 />
这次我也就原谅你了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />以后不能再做这种事情了哦？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你都有所反省了，<delay20 />
这次我就破例原谅你。<delay40 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />可不会再有下一次了哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>